*****************************************************************************************************
digiKam 5.7.0 - Release date: 2017-07-23

NEW FEATURES:

General     : Add online handbook reader not dependant of desktop.
General     : New tool to export albums by email.
Genreal     : Send by Mail tool can remove all metadat to attached items.
ImageEditor : Add SendByMail tool support.
Showfoto    : Add SendByMail tool support.
LightTable  : Add SendByMail tool support.

